Hello, i cannot add rows after closing and reopening a file
```
 let FILENAME = 'C:\\Temp\\test.xlsx';
    let workbook: Excel.Workbook = new Excel.Workbook();
    let worksheet = workbook.addWorksheet();
    worksheet.columns = [
        { header: 'BO', key: 'BO', width: 30 }
    ];
    worksheet.addRows([{ 'BO': 1 }, { 'BO': 2 }]);
    await workbook.xlsx.writeFile(FILENAME);
    workbook = await workbook.xlsx.readFile(FILENAME);
    worksheet = workbook.getWorksheet(1);
    worksheet.addRows([{ 'BO': 3 }, { 'BO': 4 }]);
    await workbook.xlsx.writeFile(FILENAME);
```
File contains only 3 rows ( + header)at the end.
Kind Regards,
G.Georgiev
